'''羅素·喬治·托維'''（'''Russell George Tovey'''，1981年11月14日出生） <ref>[http://www.whatsonstage.com/interviews/theatre/london/E8821135245224/20+Questions+With...Russell+Tovey.html "20 Questions With...Russell Tovey." What's On Stage. 3 January 2006.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110302211640/http://www.whatsonstage.com/interviews/theatre/london/E8821135245224/20+Questions+With...Russell+Tovey.html |date=2011年3月2日 }} Accessed 2011-03-22.</ref>是一位英國演員，出演了不少電視節目、電影和舞台劇。托維最知名於出演在2008年開始的BBC超自然戲劇《[[魔性人心|魔性人心]]》的[[狼人|狼人]]{{en-link|喬治·斯丹茨|George Sands}}。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/37352/being-human-returns-bbc-america-july-24th |title=Being Human Returns to BBC America 24 July |accessdate=2012-01-16 |archive-date=2018-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180803194052/https://www.dreadcentral.com/news/37352/first-artwork-for-bates-motel-checks-in/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2011年11月，托維宣布將離開《魔性人心》以專心演出BBC 3情景喜劇《[[他_&_她|他 & 她]]》。<ref name="ToveyLeaves">[http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2011/nov/12/russell-tovey-why-im-leaving-being-human Iqbal, Nosheen. "Russell Tovey: Why I'm Leaving ''Being Human'' (and Loving ''Him & Her'')." ''The Guardian.'' 11 November 2011.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2011/nov/12/russell-tovey-why-im-leaving-being-human |date=20170404160714 }} Accessed 2011-11-12.</ref>他的其他著名角色包括[[HBO|HBO]]原创剧集《[[尋_(電視劇)|寻]]》中的凯文，以及《[[神探夏洛克|神探夏洛克]]》第二季第二集中的{{en-link|亨利·奈特|List of Sherlock characters}}。

== 生平 ==
托維是Tovey Carole née Haynes (娘家姓Webb) 和喬治·托維的兩個孩子中的弟弟，他的哥哥叫丹尼爾。<ref name="NiceGuy">{{Cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/profiles/more-mr-nice-guy-why-everyone-loves-russell-tovey-2067802.html |title=Mclean, Craig. "More Mr Nice Guy: Why Everyone Loves Russell Tovey." ''The Independent.'' 5 September 2010. |access-date=2012-01-16 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125035152/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/profiles/more-mr-nice-guy-why-everyone-loves-russell-tovey-2067802.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他成長於[[Billericay|Billericay]], Essex,<ref name="Teg 2009-03-17">{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/theatre/drama/5001850/Russell-Tovey-interview-A-History-Boy-with-a-big-future.html |title=Russell Tovey interview: A History Boy with a big future |work=The Daily Telegraph |location=UK |date=2009-03-17 |accessdate=2009-03-18 |first=Byrony |last=Gordon |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126041054/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/theatre/drama/5001850/Russell-Tovey-interview-A-History-Boy-with-a-big-future.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他的父母在那裡開[[客車|客車]]，把乘客從Essex送到[[格域機場|格域機場]]，<ref name="RandallInterview">Randall, Lee. "Russell Tovey: Star Pupil." ''[[The_Scotsman|The Scotsman]].'' February 2, 2009.</ref>他也在那裡上了[[Shenfield_High_School|申菲爾德高中]]。<ref name="Taxi">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-1306082/In-taxi--actor-Russell-Tovey.html#ixzz1HMeCWjRO |title=Wilson, Benji. "In a Taxi With...Actor Russell Tovey." ''Daily Mail.'' 28 August 2010. |access-date=2012-01-16 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310064142/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-1306082/In-taxi--actor-Russell-Tovey.html#ixzz1HMeCWjRO |dead-url=no }}</ref>托維說自己小時候非常喜歡收集各種東西，喜歡與別人交流潮流信息。<ref name="RandallInterview" />他的父母支持他的愛好，帶他到考古挖掘現場和博物館，給他買金屬探測器，讓他參加挖掘考古學大會。<ref name="RandallInterview" />他曾想當歷史教師。<ref name="RandallInterview" />但在看到《[[死亡詩社|死亡詩社]]》、''[[The_Goonies|The Goonies]]''和''[[Stand_By_Me_(film)|Stand By Me]]''之後，他決定成為一名演員。<ref name="RandallInterview" />

== 生涯 == 
托維從當兒童演員開始了生涯。他參加了當地的戲劇俱樂部，吸引了一名星探的注意。<ref name="Teg 2009-03-17" />他從11歲開始表演。<ref name="RandallInterview" />他的電視生涯開始於1994年，第一次是演出兒童電視台[[CBBC|CBBC]]的''[[Mud_(TV_series)|Mud]]''。<ref name="Teg 2009-03-17"/> 

他16歲離開高中，開始在[[Barking_College|巴金大學]]參加[[Business_and_Technology_Education_Council|Btec]]表演藝術的課程.<ref name="Taxi" />他由於拒絕在學校演出一個角色而進行一個付費的表演，入學一年後被開除。<ref name="Taxi" />他在[[Chichester|Chichester]]戲劇中表演，導演是[[Debra_Gillett|黛布拉·吉列]]，[[Patrick_Marber|派屈克·馬波爾]]的妻子。<ref name="Teg 2009-03-17"/> 他遇到了Marber through Gillett，馬波爾讓他在國家劇院的演出了''Howard Katz''。<ref name="Teg 2009-03-17"/>他也在''[[His_Girl_Friday|His Girl Friday]]''和《[[黑暗物質三部曲|黑暗物質三部曲]]》中演出。<ref name="Teg 2009-03-17"/>
2004年他在[[Alan_Bennett|阿蘭·貝內特]]位於[[Royal_National_Theatre|皇家劇院]]舉行的的演出''[[The_History_Boys|The History Boys]]''中出演了Rudge一角色，之後去了Broadway, Sydney, [[惠靈頓|惠靈頓]]和香港演出了這個角色，又在該劇廣播和電影改編版本中飾演了同樣的角色。<ref name="Broadway">{{ibdb name|id=412506}}. Accessed 5 November 2006</ref><ref name="National Theatre">[http://www.nationaltheatre.org.uk/?lid=7785  ''The History Boys'' 2004] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nationaltheatre.org.uk/?lid=7785 |date=20040806124653 }}, ''[[Royal_National_Theatre|皇家劇院]]''. Accessed 17 October 2006</ref><ref name="Sydney">{{cite news | url = http://www.smh.com.au/news/arts-reviews/the-history-boys/2006/02/13/1139679513099.html | title = ''The History Boys'' | work = The Sydney Morning Herald | accessdate = 2006-10-17 | date = 2006-03-09 | archive-date = 2015-11-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151102135757/http://www.smh.com.au/news/arts-reviews/the-history-boys/2006/02/13/1139679513099.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Wellington">{{cite news | url = http://nbr.co.nz/smythe/2006/02/nziaf-history-boys-more-is-more.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080118191504/http://nbr.co.nz/smythe/2006/02/nziaf-history-boys-more-is-more.html | archivedate = 2008-01-18 | title = ''The History Boys'': More is more | accessdate = 2006-10-17 | deadurl = yes }}</ref> 他原本飾演Crowther，但在Bennett 保證（beef up）後同意演出Rudge。<ref name="RandallInterview" />不保證是因為他沒有像別人一樣上戲劇學校，他參加了由皇家劇院提供的講習班和閱讀讀物。<ref name="RandallInterview" />

2007年春天，托維在[[BBC_Three|BBC Three]]喜劇''[[Rob_Brydon's_Annually_Retentive|Rob Brydon's Annually Retentive]]''飾演了一個常设角色，扮演Rob的同性戀老闆Ben。<ref name="RandallInterview" />同年，他在BBC Three的喜劇''[[Gavin_&_Stacey|Gavin & Stacey]]''的5集中客串Budgie，Gavin 和 Smithy的朋友。之後演出了DW聖誕節特輯"[[Voyage_of_the_Damned_(Doctor_Who)|Voyage of the Damned]]"。<ref name="RandallInterview" />這個節目的執行出品人和首席編劇Russell T Davies建議讓托維接替David Tennant，而之後宣布由Matt Smith接任。托維在2009/2010《[[異世奇人|異世奇人]]》聖誕節特輯''[[The_End_of_Time|The End of Time]]''中復演了[[Midshipman|Midshipman]] Alonso Frame的角色。

托維在《[[魔性人心|魔性人心]]》中演了三個超自然室友之一[[狼人|狼人]] [[George_Sands|喬治·斯丹茨]]。試播集在2008年2月18日於BBC 3首播。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2007/11_november/06/human.shtml |title=BBC Three presents ''Being Human'' |date=2007-11-06 |publisher=BBC Three |location=UK |accessdate=2008-02-05 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126013324/http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2007/11_november/06/human.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref> A six-part series was commissioned with the first episode broadcast on 25 January 2009.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2008/04_april/24/human.shtml |title=''Being Human'' commissioned for BBC Three |publisher=BBC Three |location=UK |date=2008-04-24 |accessdate=2009-02-19 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126024031/http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2008/04_april/24/human.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2009年3月，[[Royal_Court_Theatre|Royal Court Theatre]]的''A Miracle''演出了主演Gary Trudgill，一個從外國回到Norfolk的英國士兵。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/stage/2009/mar/05/miracle-review-royal-court-london |title=Theatre review: ''A Miracle'' / Royal Court, London |work=The Guardian |location=UK |date=2009-03-05 |accessdate=2009-03-12 |first=Michael |last=Billington |archive-date=2009-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090325072457/http://www.guardian.co.uk/stage/2009/mar/05/miracle-review-royal-court-london |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="A Miracle">{{cite web |url=http://www.royalcourttheatre.com/whatson01.asp?play=540 |title=''A Miracle'' |publisher=[[Royal_Court_Theatre|Royal Court Theatre]] |accessdate=2009-03-12 |date=March 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120909153150/http://www.royalcourttheatre.com/whatson01.asp?play=540 |archivedate=2012-09-09 }}</ref>2009年3月8日，他在上為[[Margaret_Tyzack|Margaret Tyzack]]由於她在''[[The_Chalk_Garden|The Chalk Garden]]''中的表演位於[[Grosvenor_House|Grosvenor House]]頒獎。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.whatsonstage.com/index.php?pg=207&story=E8821236605695 |title=Olivier Goss: What We Heard in the Ballroom??? |work=What's On Stage |date=2009-03-08 |accessdate=2009-03-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110616100448/http://www.whatsonstage.com/index.php?pg=207&story=E8821236605695 |archivedate=2011-06-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.officiallondontheatre.co.uk/news/latest/view/item104631/Tyzack-and-Jacobi-scoop-top-honours/ |title=Tyzack and Jacobi scoop top honours |work=Official London Theatre |date=2009-03-08 |accessdate=2009-03-12 |archive-date=2010-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101221224631/http://officiallondontheatre.co.uk/news/latest/view/item104631/Tyzack-and-Jacobi-scoop-top-honours/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2009年，托維工作於電影''[[Huge_(film)|Huge]]''<ref>[http://www.screendaily.com/news/production/uk-ireland/uk-comedy-huge-starts-shooting-in-london/5002516.article UK comedy ''Huge'' starts shooting in London] {{Wayback|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/production/uk-ireland/uk-comedy-huge-starts-shooting-in-london/5002516.article |date=20191208224036 }}, ''Screen Daily'', 17 June 2009. Accessed 27 August 2009</ref>並演出了兩個電視試播集：''Young, Unemployed and Lazy'' (BBC 3情景喜劇),<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2009/may/12/bbc-russell-tovey-bedroom-comedy |title=Russell Tovey to star in BBC3 sitcom that never leaves the bedroom |work=The Guardian |location=UK |date=2009-05-12 |accessdate=2009-05-12 |first=Leigh |last=Holmwood |archive-date=2011-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111224193732/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2009/may/12/bbc-russell-tovey-bedroom-comedy |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bigtalkproductions.com/index.php/in-production/young-unemployed-and-lazy |title=Young, Unemployed and Lazy |publisher=Big Talk Productions |accessdate=2009-06-22 }} {{Dead link|date=September 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref> ，之後在2010年改名成''[[Him_&_Her_(TV_series)|Him & Her]]''<ref name="HimAndHer">{{cite web |title=Him & Her |url=http://www.him-and-her.com |work=Him and Her |date=2010-06-10 |accessdate=2010-06-20 |archive-date=2013-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207074840/http://him-and-her.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和''[[The_Increasingly_Poor_Decisions_of_Todd_Margaret|The Increasingly Poor Decisions of Todd Margaret]]'' (part of ''[[Comedy_Showcase|Comedy Showcase]]'')，一個英國電視第四台喜劇，與[[Spike_Jonze|斯派克·姜茲]] 和[[Will_Arnett|威爾·阿納特]]一起，編劇是[[David_Cross|大衛·科茨]] 和[[Shaun_Pye|肖恩·派伊]]。<ref name="Todd">{{cite web |url=http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/spike-jonze-to-star-in-c4-comedy/5001616.article |title=Spike Jonze to star in C4 comedy |work=Broadcast Now |date=2009-05-15 |accessdate=2009-05-29 |archive-date=2019-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205211913/https://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/spike-jonze-to-star-in-c4-comedy/5001616.article |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Todd2">{{cite web |url=http://www.channel4.com/programmes/comedy-showcase/episode-guide/series-9/episode-1 |title=Comedy Showcase |work=Comedy Showcase |date=2009-11-27 |accessdate=2009-11-27 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234056/http://www.channel4.com/programmes/comedy-showcase/episode-guide/series-9/episode-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

